		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_BUILD_AMERICAN_FORT_REC">
			<Text>It will improve the [ICON_STRENGTH] Defense of any military unit stationed in this tile and cause damage to enemy units that end their turn adjacent.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CIV5_IMPROVEMENTS_AMERICAN_FORT_TEXT">
